          }
        },
        "row_WfFd7T": {
          "type": "row",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/ertr.jpg",
            "caption": "",
            "heading": "What's the Difference Between a Sports Steering Wheel and a Basic One?",
            "text": "<p>With its reduced diameter and <strong>contoured grips</strong>, a sports steering wheel improves responsiveness. Premium materials (Nappa leather, Alcantara) resist wear while maintaining a firm grip — ideal for corner exit acceleration. Compatible with most <strong>automatic</strong> and manual gearboxes.</p>",
            "button_label": "",
