    "rich_text_PdbVCT": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_PbznYU": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How to Know If a Steering Wheel Fits Your Car?",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "text_jKFxzy": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Check the manufacturing year, power steering type, and airbag connector. Our kits include a universal adapter for recent BMW 3 Series, Mercedes A-Class (after 2018), and Volkswagen Golf VII+.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading_PbznYU",
        "text_jKFxzy"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "desktop_content_position": "center",
        "content_alignment": "center",
        "color_scheme": "",
        "full_width": true,
        "padding_top": 40,
        "padding_bottom": 52
      }
    },
    "rich_text_4LAEJX": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_N9cCHb": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What Is the Best Steering Wheel for Your Car?",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "text_cMCCTE": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Choosing the <strong>best car steering wheel</strong> depends on your make, model, and what you're after: more sportiness, the perfect grip with Alcantara or perforated leather, larger paddle shifters, a racing flat-bottom design, or integrated heating for winter. At Drive Custom, we offer premium custom steering wheels with plug & play compatibility for the leading German brands.</p><h2>Top Aftermarket Steering Wheels to Transform Your Interior</h2><p>Here is our selection of the best car steering wheels right now, tested and approved by thousands of enthusiasts:</p><ul><li><strong>For Audi</strong>: The <a href=\"https://drivecustom.co.uk/products/volant-audi-a-trois\">Audi A3/RS3/S3 steering wheel</a> with a flat-bottom design, carbon fibre inserts, and contrast stitching is an absolute best-seller. Incredible grip and an ultra-sporty look guaranteed! A1 owners are not left out with the <a href=\"https://drivecustom.co.uk/products/volant-audi-a-un\">Audi A1/S1 steering wheel</a>, more compact but just as premium.</li><li><strong>For BMW</strong>: The <a href=\"https://drivecustom.co.uk/products/volant-bmw-serie-un\">BMW 1 Series steering wheel</a> in Alcantara with oversized paddle shifters instantly transforms your compact into a true M Performance machine.</li><li><strong>For Mercedes</strong>: Nothing beats the <a href=\"https://drivecustom.co.uk/products/volant-mercedes-classe-a\">Mercedes A-Class steering wheel</a> with its AMG-inspired design, haptic controls, and flawless Nappa leather finish for daily sporty luxury.</li><li><strong>For Volkswagen</strong>: GTI/R fans are massively upgrading to the <a href=\"https://drivecustom.co.uk/products/volant-golf-sept\">Golf 7/7.5/8 steering wheel</a> with flat-bottom R design, 12 o'clock marker, and extended paddles — probably the best value for money on the market.</li></ul><h2>How to Know Which Steering Wheel Is Best for YOU?</h2><p>The \"best\" car steering wheel is the one that perfectly matches your driving needs:<br/>- Daily driving → go for heated leather and full multifunction controls.<br/>- Track days and winding roads → choose Alcantara or carbon fibre with a pronounced flat bottom.<br/>- No-compromise racing look → oversized paddles + LED shift lights if available.</p><p>All our steering wheels are 100% compatible with original airbags, virtual cockpit/iDrive/MBUX, and can be fitted in 30-45 minutes with our detailed tutorials.</p><p>Ready to take it to the next level? Browse our selection and find the car steering wheel that will completely transform your interior!</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading_N9cCHb",
        "text_cMCCTE"
      ],
